name: Validate Row level delete icon on  Manage User Page
description:
As a Admin
I want to able to navigate to the 'Manage User' page 
So that I can access its deleting functionality

steps.name: Given  Admin is on dashboard page after Login and clicks User on the navigation bar
When  Admin clicks the delete icon on row level in Manage User Page
Then  Admin should see a alert open with heading Confirm along with  <YES> and <NO> button for deletion
